cs.SI, cs.CL, cs.CY, cs.SD, cs.IR 

This paper focuses on analyzing social signals and content in online discussions on Reddit, which involves natural language processing and sentiment analysis (cs.CL), as well as data mining and machine learning techniques (cs.SI). The paper also discusses the differences in communities on Reddit, which could fall under the categories of cyberculture (cs.CY) and social network analysis (cs.SD). Finally, the paper involves analyzing and predicting user behavior, which could fall under the category of information retrieval (cs.IR).
